{"type":"message","id":"380fe29d","parentId":"9c5eef00","timestamp":"2026-04-15T02:17:58.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me compare the current sessions list against the last known state.\n\nLast checked: 2026-04-15T02:11:00Z\nCurrent time: 2026-04-15 02:16 UTC\n\nLet me compare session statuses:\n\n1. **cron:6f3323ef** (DTLX 5p Monitor) — running ✅ (still running)\n2. **cron:ed2d0b5d** (QLHV 5p monitor) — status was \"running\" at 02:11, updatedAt was 1776214290785 (which is ~02:04 UTC). Now updatedAt is 1776219091114 (which is ~02:11 UTC). \n\nSo it was running before and is still running now — this is the parent cron that spawned sub-agents and restarted its cycle at 02:03 UTC. It's still active.\n\n3. **cron:e7885813** (Agent Status to Lead) — was running at 02:11, still running now (updatedAt: 1776218652404, which is ~02:10 UTC). Still alive.\n\n4. **cron:ac986a8d** — still marked as orphaned and stale, hasn't changed.\n\n5. **cron:53c5832a** (Daily Briefing) — completed as expected.\n\n6. **main** session — appears to be done as well.\n\n7. **telegram:direct:6053576134** — done, ended around 01:16 UTC.\n\n8. **telegram:group:-5163901258** (QLHV group) — was done at 01:11 UTC, updatedAt shows 1776219281472 which converts to approximately 02:14 UTC, so it received activity more recently than the other sessions.\n\nLooking at the session list, this QLHV group session shows as \"done\" status but with a recent updatedAt timestamp, which suggests it's still being actively polled or has pending messages despite being marked as finished.\n\nComparing to the last heartbeat state at 02:11 UTC, the cron jobs are all stable and the orphaned session remains unchanged. The timestamp discrepancy on the QLHV session appears to be normal polling behavior rather than new activity, so there don't seem to be any actual changes to report. The pipeline is still healthy with no new failures or blockers, so I'll stay silent and update the heartbeat state instead. The cron:ac986a8d process is still stuck after over 13 hours, so there's no real change to report—the pipeline remains in a degraded state but nothing new has occurred.","thinkingSignature":"fce01caa442e84d29fbf6580cb2842291737dbf0ddbb7b5620048f1dbb0a8679"},{"type":"text","text":"\nComparing current state against `heartbeat-state.json` (last checked: 02:11 UTC).\n\n**Key sessions status:**\n- `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p) — running ✅\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p) — running ✅  \n- `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status) — running ✅\n- `cron:ac986a8d` — still orphaned (no change)\n- All child subagents — same failed/done states (no new failures)\n\nNo new changes detected. Pipeline status unchanged. Staying silent."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":11534,"output":671,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":407,"totalTokens":26556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776219453918,"responseId":"062e283ef8da5868bad39a53b0752172"}}
